data.text:
Ginsberg by Others Subseries 1.1575469

Container Summary: 20 manuscript boxes, 1 half manuscript box (10.25 linear ft.)

Scope and Contents note

Subseries 1.1 Ginsberg by Others is arranged chronologically and contains photographic prints of Ginsberg from 1926 thru 1997.

Allen Ginsberg (Also See: Mexico - 1955 [Pics Not By Allen]) 575831 1955 - 1959

Scope and Contents note

Includes image of Montgomery St. room, San Francisco where 'Howl' was composed and images from Allen Ginsberg's time in Paris

Photographs by Others Subseries 1.2575311

Container Summary: 4 manuscript boxes, 1 half manuscript box, 2 flat boxes (4.25 linear ft.)

Scope and Contents note

Subseries 1.2 Photographs by Others contains two subsubseries, oversized prints and alphabetical file arranged alphabetically by photographer -where identified. Please note: this subseries does include some images of Ginsberg. Oversized prints have been removed and housed in flat boxes.
